SQL_STMT_U.val: select isn , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@aShortDescription)[1]', 'varchar(200)') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@aLongDescription)[1]', 'varchar(1000)') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@aAddress)[1]', 'varchar(200)') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@aLocation)[1]', 'varchar(100)') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@aCity)[1]', 'varchar(100)') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@aPostCode)[1]', 'varchar(9)') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@aEventImage)[1]', 'varchar(1000)') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@aEventUrl)[1]', 'varchar(1000)') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@dStartDate)[1]', 'varchar(11)') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@dEndDate)[1]', 'varchar(11)') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@nCategory)[1]', 'int') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@nCurrencyIsn)[1]', 'int') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@tFromTime)[1]', 'varchar(8)') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@tToTime)[1]', 'varchar(8)') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@aContactEmail)[1]', 'varchar(100)') , cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@aContactNumber)[1]', 'varchar(50)') , case cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@lPublish)[1]', 'varchar(3)') when 'NO' then 0 else 1 end , case cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@lFeature)[1]', 'varchar(3)') when 'NO' then 0 else 1 end from eo where eo_type = 2280 and long_name like ':1' and isn in (select eo2_isn from relations where relation_type = 2712 and eo1_isn = :2) order by cast(long_comment as xml).value('(/a/@dStartDate)[1]', 'varchar(11)')

Text.val: eoIsn can be either from the location city/region or from the entity id
